  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"pUGaSVBT\">这种事关人家生命健康人生未来的文件，撰写人粗心，审核人马虎，哪怕就是写错或者漏掉那么几个字，后果都不堪设想。</p><p data-pid=\"ujlzoDn2\">想想看，如果法官判决死刑，分管副院长案卷都没看就签批，判下来被告没上诉，报最高院核准后回来交付执行，人打掉以后承办法官才发现自己当时少写了六个字:<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=474726097&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%BC%93%E6%9C%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">缓期二年执行<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</p><p data-pid=\"s84SdoQg\">那可就太刺激了。</p><p data-pid=\"U63Stzep\">当然，这是玩笑，但是法官算错被告人刑期导致罪犯提前释放的案子是有的：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ebb92594a542a9a0edbaab11e02b7127_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"743\" data-rawheight=\"384\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-ebb92594a542a9a0edbaab11e02b7127\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-da8020c67d1f93d9f90be94242703211_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"743\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-ebb92594a542a9a0edbaab11e02b7127_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ebb92594a542a9a0edbaab11e02b7127_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"743\" data-rawheight=\"384\" data-size=\"normal\